{"text_id":164323,"tokens":["Alright",","," so"," let","'","s"," dive"," into"," this"," topic"," about"," charter"," schools"," and"," school"," vouchers"," in"," the"," United"," States","."," It","'","s"," a"," bit"," of"," a"," complex"," subject",","," but"," I","'","ll"," try"," to"," break"," it"," down"," in"," a"," simple"," way",".","\n\n","First"," off",","," charter"," schools"," are"," kind"," of"," like"," public"," schools",","," but"," with"," a"," twist","."," They"," are"," publicly"," funded",","," which"," means"," they"," get"," money"," from"," the"," government"," just"," like"," regular"," public"," schools","."," However",","," they"," operate"," independently"," of"," the"," traditional"," public"," school"," system","."," This"," means"," they"," have"," more"," freedom"," to"," try"," out"," new"," teaching"," methods",","," cur","ricul","ums",","," and"," management"," styles","."," They"," are"," usually"," established"," by"," a"," charter",","," which"," is"," a"," sort"," of"," contract"," that"," outlines"," the"," school","'","s"," mission",","," program",","," students"," served",","," performance"," goals",","," and"," methods"," of"," assessment","."," Because"," they"," have"," this"," flexibility",","," charter"," schools"," can"," sometimes"," offer"," a"," more"," innovative"," or"," specialized"," education"," compared"," to"," standard"," public"," schools","."," But",","," they"," are"," still"," held"," accountable"," for"," academic"," results"," and"," upholding"," the"," promises"," made"," in"," their"," charters",".","\n\n","Now",","," school"," vouchers"," are"," a"," bit"," different","."," A"," school"," voucher"," is"," essentially"," a"," certificate"," of"," government"," funding"," that"," parents"," can"," use"," to"," send"," their"," child"," to"," a"," school"," of"," their"," choice",","," including"," private"," and"," sometimes"," even"," religious"," schools","."," The"," idea"," behind"," vouchers"," is"," to"," give"," parents"," more"," options"," outside"," of"," the"," public"," school"," system",","," especially"," if"," they"," feel"," that"," their"," local"," public"," schools"," are"," not"," meeting"," their"," child","'","s"," needs","."," The"," voucher"," covers"," all"," or"," part"," of"," the"," tuition"," at"," the"," chosen"," school",","," which"," can"," be"," a"," big"," help"," for"," families"," who"," might"," not"," otherwise"," afford"," private"," education",".","\n\n","So",","," how"," do"," these"," differ"," from"," the"," standard"," public"," school"," system","?"," Well",","," traditional"," public"," schools"," are"," funded"," and"," run"," by"," government"," agencies",","," usually"," at"," the"," state"," or"," local"," level","."," They"," have"," to"," follow"," a"," set"," curriculum"," and"," adhere"," to"," state"," education"," standards","."," Public"," schools"," are"," required"," to"," accept"," all"," students"," from"," their"," geographic"," area",","," which"," means"," they"," serve"," a"," diverse"," student"," body",".","\n\n","In"," contrast",","," charter"," schools",","," while"," still"," public",","," have"," more"," autonomy"," and"," can"," be"," more"," selective"," in"," their"," educational"," approaches","."," School"," vouchers",","," on"," the"," other"," hand",","," allow"," for"," public"," funding"," to"," be"," used"," for"," private"," education",","," which"," is"," a"," significant"," departure"," from"," the"," traditional"," public"," school"," model",".","\n\n","Both"," charter"," schools"," and"," school"," vouchers"," are"," part"," of"," a"," broader"," movement"," to"," increase"," school"," choice"," and"," improve"," educational"," outcomes"," by"," introducing"," competition"," and"," innovation"," into"," the"," education"," system","."," However",","," they"," are"," also"," subjects"," of"," debate","."," Supporters"," argue"," that"," they"," provide"," valuable"," alternatives"," to"," failing"," public"," schools"," and"," give"," parents"," more"," control"," over"," their"," children","'","s"," education","."," Critics",","," however",","," worry"," that"," they"," divert"," much","-","needed"," funds"," away"," from"," public"," schools"," and"," can"," lead"," to"," greater"," inequality"," in"," the"," education"," system",".","\n\n","So",","," there"," you"," have"," it","!"," Charter"," schools"," and"," school"," vouchers"," are"," two"," different"," ways"," to"," approach"," education"," reform"," in"," the"," U",".","S",".,"," each"," with"," its"," own"," set"," of"," advantages"," and"," challenges"," compared"," to"," the"," traditional"," public"," school"," system","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"gpt4o","label":1}